text:
Amazing nail art, right!
Asahi-chan, are you going to do it too?

Well...
Asahi has a photoshoot tomorrow, so...
Eh, I want to do something~
If you remove it right away, it's fine.
Then, just care for them or something.
If it's hair styling or something.

Sure!
I want you to do something amazing!!

Oh, that's a good idea!
Asahi-chan, come here~

...?
I'm properly trimming my nails, you know.

That sounds fun too!
How about it, Asahi-chan?

I'm fine with it but...
I get sleepy when my hair is touched.
